Title: Cracking Cogchewer
Description:
Cogchewer is muscle for Candle King. So mean! Rebuilds earthen gears for wars. Also in charge of mine's defenses. 

Need his keys to get in the mines... and get me out of this thing!
ObjectivesText: Kill Cogchewer in the Lost Mines and recover his keys.
RewardText: Thank you, $n. Never thought I walk free again.
